'''Jasmina Tinjić''' is a professional [[Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnian]] tennis player playing in the ITF Women's Circuit. On July 4, 2011, she reached her highest [[Women's Tennis Association|WTA]] singles ranking of 257. On August 8, 2011, she also reached her highest [[Women's Tennis Association|WTA]] doubles ranking of 521. She is coached by Jusuf Tinjić.
