'''Karihaugen''' is a neighbourhood in the residential area of [[Ellingsrud]] in [[Oslo]], [[Norway]].<ref name=snl>{{cite encyclopedia|year=2010|title=Ellingsrud|encyclopedia=[[Store norske leksikon]]|author=Engstrøm, Bjørn|editor=Tvedt, Knut Are|publisher=Kunnskapsforlaget|location=Oslo|url=http://snl.no/Ellingsrud|language=Norwegian|accessdate=10 November 2010}}</ref> The development of the area started in the 1970s.<ref name=snl/>

