{{Infobox person |image = | | | name = Siobhan Marshall | birth_name = | birth_date = | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | deathcause = | occupation = [[Actress]] | yearsactive = 2004 - present | spouse = | website = }}
'''Siobhan Marshall''' is a [[New Zealand]] actress best known for her role as [[Pascalle West]] from the comedy/drama series [[Outrageous Fortune (TV series)|Outrageous Fortune]].
Marshall attended [[Auckland]]’s [[Unitec New Zealand|Unitec]] School of Performing Screen Arts and graduated in 2003. In 2004, Siobhan appeared on [[Shortland Street]], playing a character coincidentally called Siobhan.
Marshall has also appeared in the kid's show ''[[Amazing Extraordinary Friends]]'' for one episode as "Dominique". She has also starred in the celebrity singing show [[Sing Like A Superstar]] and won the competition.
Marshall stands at 183&nbsp;cm (6&nbsp;ft.).
