{{Politics of Bosnia and Herzegovina}}
An '''[[independence referendum]]''' was held in [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] between 29 February and 1 March 1992.<ref>[[Dieter Nohlen|Nohlen, D]] & Stöver, P (2010) ''Elections in Europe: A data handbook'', p330 ISBN 978-3-8329-5609-7</ref> The result was 99.7% in favour with a 63.6% voter turnout.<ref>Nohlen & Stöver, p334</ref> Independence was strongly favoured by [[Bosniaks]] and [[Bosnian Croat]] voters, but the referendum was largely boycotted by [[Bosnian Serbs]].<ref>[http://www.insightonconflict.org/conflicts/bosnia-herzegovina/conflict-profile/conflicttimeline/ Bosnia and Herzegovina] Insight on Conflict</ref>
