{{Infobox spacecraft
| Name                   = Korabl-Sputnik 2
| Major_Contractors      = [[OKB-1]]
| Bus                    = [[Vostok (spacecraft)|Vostok-1K]]
| Mission_Type           = Biological<br/>Technology
| Launch Date            = {{start-date|19 August 1960, 08:44:06|timezone=yes}}&nbsp;UTC
| Carrier_Rocket         = [[Vostok-L]] 8K72
| Flight Number          = {{nowrap|[[serial number|s/n]] L1-12}}
| Launch_Site            = [[Baikonur Cosmodrome|Baikonur]] [[Gagarin's Start|Site 1/5]]
| Decay                  = {{end-date|20 August 1960, 06:00:00|timezone=yes}}&nbsp;UTC
| Mission_Duration       = 1 day
| COSPAR_ID              = 1960 Lambda 1 |nolink = on
| Mass                   = {{convert|4600|kg}}
| Periapsis              = {{convert|287|km}}
| Apoapsis               = {{convert|324|km}}
| Inclination            = 64.95°
| Period                 = 90.72 minutes
